The iconic design details of the polo shirt are brought to the wrist with a sleek and modern reinterpretation of the Lacoste.12.12 for her. A petit-piqué pattern on the outer of the bold curved dial and the center of the silicone strap provides eye-catching detail, while a crocodile at 3 o’clock adds signature Lacoste branding. Offered in a choice of monochrome colors, the watch is complete with hands and stick indexes in polished metal for a feminine touch. 2-year international warranty.
Futuristic aromatic fragrance born from the clash between luxury craftmanship and new tech. A bold scent with notes of addictive creamy lavender, energising lemon and sexy, woody vanilla.

products.nameEn: ARMANI CODE PARFUM -Eau De Parfum- 75 ML
products.descriptionEn: Fragrance for men with aromatic and woody notes,for a powerful and sensual trail.

Lacoste reinvents the Lacoste.12.12 for a new generation as it reinterprets the brand’s signature watch in a sleek and minimalist design. With a new rounded and faceted case and matt-finish bezel, the three-hand timepiece is offered in a choice of monochrome colors including the classic Lacoste green. Inspired by the iconic polo shirt, the timepiece features a crocodile at 3 o’clock, and a petit piqué pattern at the center of the silicone strap and the outer of the bold curved dial. 2-year international warranty.
